Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:14.77,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.77,0:00:17.11,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire and earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:19.50,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Water and dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:23.05,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unwilling hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:24.28,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:26.67,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend write itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:29.08,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,History build itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:32.78,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The future is our adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:33.87,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Make!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.87,0:00:36.27,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The light live,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:38.67,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightnings talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:42.40,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.46,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:45.87,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow your path,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:49.45,Eng OP,,0000,0000,0000,,And watch your future,
